* Pierre Boulez: &quot;...explosante-fixe...&quot;, version for two flutes, MIDI-flute, electronics, and orchestra (1993)
* Pierre Boulez: &quot;Répons&quot;, for six soloists, chamber ensemble, electronic sounds, and live electronics (1981–1984)
