<doc id="259080" wikidata="Q261326" url="?curid=259080" title="Altmühltal">
<text>Altmühltal (lit.: &quot;Altmühl valley&quot;) is a &quot;Verwaltungsgemeinschaft&quot; (federation of municipalities) in the district of Weißenburg-Gunzenhausen in Bavaria in Germany. It consists of the following municipalities:
*Alesheim 
*Dittenheim
*Markt Berolzheim
*Meinheim

