*&quot;&quot; (1986) 
*&quot;Public Eye: An Investigation Into the Disappearance of the World&quot; (1990) 
*&quot;Gender Wars: A Novel and Some Conversation About Sex and Gender&quot; (1994) 
*&quot;The Last of the Lumbermen&quot; (2013) 
*&quot;A Blue Spruce Christmas&quot; (2010) 

