<doc id="259152" wikidata="Q5589721" url="?curid=259152" title="Governor of Taiwan">
<text>Governor of Taiwan may refer to:

* Governor of Formosa, appointed during the Dutch rule period
* Governor of Fujian-Taiwan (), appointed during the late Qing rule period
* Governor-General of Taiwan, appointed during the Japanese rule period
* Governor of Taiwan Province, appointed during the Republic of China period
* A hypothetical Governor of Taiwan Provincial People&#x27;s Government claimed by the People&#x27;s Republic of China</text><links>
